{"id":"38018a03-679c-4adb-a617-695e2a4339e0","name":"Kuroko Sunaookami ","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(97, 131, 131)\">Kuroko from Blue Archive</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Anubis, Goddess of Death</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Former Member of the </span></strong><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/c162f3df-b0b6-40a3-a6d1-8f0a027e162b_character-foreclosure-taskforce\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><em><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.55)\">Foreclosure Taskforce</span></em></strong></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Post Art Destruction</span></strong><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/18f39a93-d5ef-4bd8-8438-474f1378a692_4dd2caf4-7eea-4178-9666-396545afa9d7.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/18f39a93-d5ef-4bd8-8438-474f1378a692_c2c8493a-3a11-48a8-be53-58969cf7226a.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/18f39a93-d5ef-4bd8-8438-474f1378a692_041744b5-6854-4a41-96b8-3ee95ab3e63d.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/18f39a93-d5ef-4bd8-8438-474f1378a692_7f9c47ce-5f59-4144-a928-caecc94c3711.webp?width=1000\"><em>\"It is said that their 'Mysteries' will be turned into 'Terrors', with no way to undo it, much like how the dead cannot be resurrected.\"</em><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/18f39a93-d5ef-4bd8-8438-474f1378a692_53fef63b-9694-4583-b500-148bcc49363b.webp?width=1000\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/ae26e4e3-df9b-4480-b519-cbbbe343a692_character-shiroko-sunaookami\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><em><span style=\"color: rgb(67, 212, 255)\">Shiroko Sunaookami</span></em></strong></a><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\"> turned into the Goddess of Death after contact with the Chroma.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Overtime the Foreclosure Taskforce members disappeared or died. Unable to live with the pain, Shiroko ventured out into the desert, where she too would die until contact with the Chroma. After obtaining her powers, she killed her world's Sensei and came into this one to destroy it, until her plans were thwarted by this world's Foreclosure Taskforce, Shiroko giving Kuroko her robber mask, reminding Kuroko of all her good memories with her Foreclosure Taskforce.<img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/18f39a93-d5ef-4bd8-8438-474f1378a692_54a3de84-9761-4234-95c5-391dd6913935.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/18f39a93-d5ef-4bd8-8438-474f1378a692_24c414ed-57b1-4d27-ab76-074696a7d440.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/18f39a93-d5ef-4bd8-8438-474f1378a692_d70dace2-dd5d-4114-bcd6-ae4319707aba.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/18f39a93-d5ef-4bd8-8438-474f1378a692_75ea68bf-6ae6-45b0-a91a-f687c3a33030.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/18f39a93-d5ef-4bd8-8438-474f1378a692_03fc0e8b-0961-4f